snippet.textDisplay:
Can you please stop asking to like and subscribe at the beginning? Shouldn’t you be asking that at the end?
The new viewers have never seen any of your videos, yet immediately into the video, you ask people to like and subscribe. A normal viewer would have either skipped through the beginning or clicked off the video. Others may actually like and subscribe, but that’s just easy bait for you. Not saying that that’s wrong for people to do, but it’s probably easier of you to tell them later at the end so that they can subscribe and like.
